race.comment: BOSS MODE (1) just ran into one better at Eagle Farm when resuming and should find this task more to his liking. Gets 2kg weight relief with the claim and looks the one they all have to run down. YEAH BUDDY (4) has placed four of five overall including one over this distance range. Ready to peak now fourth run back and can make his presence felt. BLUE WHITE BLUE (10) strips fitter second-up from the spell and gets the services of Wiggins on board from the low draw. Not to be underestimated. PRECISE TORQUE (12) gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim and looks one for the exotics players. ZHONGXIN KOALA (15) best of the rest while fresh.
